This paper discusses the evolution of computer viruses and anti-virus techniques, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the development of new methodologies by anti-virus experts, which could be related to software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper may touch upon distributed computing (cs.DC) and systems and control (cs.SI) as defensive techniques employed by anti-virus products may involve these areas.
